## Recommended Next Priorities

1. Add caregiver route (M8 + D1) — register route, enable caregiver role
2. Edit pet profile (M2) — edit mode on pet detail screen
3. Delete pet UI (M3) — swipe or menu action on dashboard
4. User profile management (M6) — edit name/photo in settings
5. Care circle management (M9 partial) — remove member, change roles

